    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels. The single below-required factor (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is offset by the strength of the quantitative output comparison (E/uval ≤ 1.74 for all QoIs) and the direct equivalence of the validation activity to the COU. The mesh convergence study demonstrated GCI < 2.1%, confirming adequate discretization control. Overall credibility is assessed as sufficient to support a Medium-risk regulatory decision.",
